name: Kamalakara
description: Once upon a time in the parallel world of wayang there was a human named Kalamakara, he was a demigod. But one day Kalamakara made a mistake that made the gods angry, finally he was exiled on a high mountain for 1000 years. Kamalakara then decided to meditate while contemplating his mistake, after meditating for 1000 years, Kalamakara was then moksha. The gods saw his determination and gave Kalamakara a mandate to protect and prosper mankind and all that is in it.
